Plymouth Rock Management Company of New Jersey: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 6:07 AM ET
Insurance

Company Overview of Plymouth Rock Management Company of New Jersey



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Plymouth Rock Management Company of New Jersey provides various auto insurance products to customers in New Jersey. The company offers auto, commercial auto, homeowners, motorcycle, boat and watercraft, motor home, collector car, and umbrella insurance policies. It sells products through independent agents and prudential financial professionals. Plymouth Rock Management Company of New Jersey was formerly known as Palisades Safety and Insurance Management Company. The company was founded in 1992 and is based in Berkeley Heights, New Jersey. Plymouth Rock Management Company of New Jersey operates as a subsidiary of The Plymouth Rock Company Incorporated.


Connell Corporate Center II200 Connell DriveSuite 3000Berkeley Heights, NJ 07922United StatesFounded in 1992



Phone: 908-790-7885

Fax: 908-790-7856

www.plymouthrock.com







