Plymouth Rock Management Company of New Jersey Key Developments

Plymouth Rock Management Co. of New Jersey Names Will Jerro as President of the Direct Division and Teachers Auto Insurance Co. of New Jersey
Jan 27 16
Plymouth Rock Management Co. of New Jersey announced that it has named Will Jerro as president of the direct division and Teachers Auto Insurance Co. of New Jersey. Jerro has more than 20 years of experience in direct-to-consumer insurance sales and marketing, including senior positions at Tranzact and Fiserv Inc. He succeeds Marc Buro, who has transitioned to his role as CEO of InsuraMatch, a Plymouth Rock-affiliated online insurance agency.


